import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Button from './Button'

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"button"}}>{`Button`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Button} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"theme"}}>{`Theme`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"red"}}>{`red`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={'<Button theme=\"red\">버튼</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
  <Button theme="red">버튼</Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"white"}}>{`white`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __code={'<Button theme=\"white\">취소</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
  <Button theme="white">취소</Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"size"}}>{`Size`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"30"}}>{`30`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __code={'<Button size={30}>작은거</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
  <Button size={30}>작은거</Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"40"}}>{`40`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={4} __code={'<Button size={40}>보통</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
  <Button size={40}>보통</Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"50"}}>{`50`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={5} __code={'<Button size={50}>큰거</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
  <Button size={50}>큰거</Button>
</Playground>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
